('e9375127-0bb0-47bc-a99c-e1d75065c157','Aragoke – koi', 'A beautiful fish', 25454000, 1, NOW()),
('a1508392-bfbc-4a6b-8242-1634b4fb4ce7', 'Saki-Hikari Multi-Season Floating Pellets', "Maintain your show-quality koi year-round - without switching food with Saki-Hikari Professional Multi-Season. Effective in water temperatures as low as 58 degrees Fahrenheit, Saki-Hikari is engineered for maximum digestibility. A special Probiotic bacteria is added for enhanced growth and digestive health. Pure-cultured spirulina is added to develop and maintain beautiful coloration. Regular use will actually improve your pond's water quality, all while promoting fat-deposit-free growth in your most beautiful koi.", 1698600, 10, NOW()),
('4b46f9ff-d875-4613-a00a-ce61732adfb3', 'Koi Food – Dainichi Premium – Floating Pellet', 'Dainichi’s standout two-step application of crucial vitamins and minerals, notably Vitamins C and E, fortifies your Koi’s vibrance, sheen, and whites, bringing out their best. As with all our products, Premium includes calcium montmorillonite clay, replicating the natural ingestion of mineral particles and working to contain metabolic toxins. Our formula is fortified with raw, full-strength vitamins, digestive enzymes, and garlic to bolster your Koi’s health and guard against internal parasites.', 2565400, 15, NOW()),
('cb214502-03ea-47ea-9e6d-c7f4457989de','Sho Koi Impact Fish Food', 'Sho Koi Impact Fish Food by Total Koi is a high quality nutritional formula for koi, goldfish, comets and other pond fish. The food pellets float and will not cloud water. These pellets are large, 5.5 mm / 0.22″ in diameter.', 1257300, 15, NOW()),
